name: 哈米什·普拉格玛斯
name_full: 哈米什·普拉格玛斯 Hamish Plaggmars

last_movies.title: 神奇数字马戏团 第一季

introduction: Hamish Plaggemars is a Melbourne-based Actor, Voice Actor, and Writer born on July 27, 1996. Hamish has been professionally acting since 2010 with appearances in films, TV series, video games, web series, and audio productions . He graduated with a Master of Screenwriting from the Victorian College of the Arts in 2019 and has developed several film and TV projects.
